(1)
Colonial Park: A view northeastward across the middle of the southern half and showing a playground at the head of West 149th Street. Buildings shown line the east side of Bradhurst Ave., north from West 148th Street.
September 1, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, slightly north. Intersection shown is West 150th Street.
September 1, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The aforementioned playground, viewed in a southward direction.
August 29, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
